   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46885303_1" alt="" width="562" height="337" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;News&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2025/russian-criminals-sanctioned-over-medibank-hack.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM25292" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Russian criminals sanctioned over Medibank hack | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.techtarget.com/searchsecurity/news/252512587/SolarWinds-hackers-still-active-using-new-techniques?utm_campaign=20220202_DeadBolt+ransomware+decryption+key+released%3B+Plus%2C+blockchain+security+best+practices&amp;amp;utm_medium=EM&amp;amp;utm_source=NLN&amp;amp;track=NL-1820&amp;amp;ad=940504&amp;amp;asrc=EM_NLN_204197264" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;SolarWinds hackers still active using new techniques&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2024/six-australians-arrested-in-sim-box-crackdown.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM22807" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Six Australians arrested in SIM box crackdown | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2024/company-loses--40m-to-deepfake-video-call.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Company loses $40m to deepfake video call scam | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.oaic.gov.au/about-us/our-regulatory-approach/guide-to-privacy-regulatory-action/chapter-6-civil-penalties" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://www.oaic.gov.au/about-us/our-regulatory-approach/guide-to-privacy-regulatory-action/chapter-6-civil-penalties&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.indusface.com/blog/what-is-a-zero-day-exploit/?utm_source=Email&amp;amp;utm_medium=LeadSquared&amp;amp;utm_campaign=blog-weekly-mailer-Jan-31" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;What is a zero day exploit?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46885304_1" alt="" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Session Topic:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this session we will be investigating common and emerging cyber security attacks and techniques.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We will be focussing specifically on the following:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Threat Vectors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Threat Actors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Threat Goals&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;How a system is infiltrated&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Out of Session Activity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Chapter&amp;nbsp;2 of Cybersecurity&amp;nbsp;Essentials - Netacad&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Read RedLegg Blog - Threat Actors &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.redlegg.com/blog/cyber-threat-actor-types" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://www.redlegg.com/blog/cyber-threat-actor-types&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portfolio Tasks:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;Check outstanding work requirements under Assessments tab.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can begin work on PART-TWO of AT1.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; text-shadow: none !important; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: small; color: #000000; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0